API Reference¶

session

The following class, RobinHood_Object, allowing users to begin and end Robinhood sessions.

user

The following class, User, is used to represent an existing Robinhod User.

portfolio

The following class, Portoflio, is used to represent an existing Robinhod user’s portfolio.

instrument

The following class, Instrument, is used to represent a tradable instrument on the Robinhood platform.

order

The following class, Order, is used to represent an order a user can place.

pyrh_redesign
